data.description: Beautiful two bedroom, 2 bath second-floor condo in fantastic and sought after neighborhood! Nicely updated bathrooms, private deck off eat-in kitchen and living room, fireplace and separate dining room. Solid core doors and private primary suite. This home is a beauty and move in ready. Quick close possible. Pets allowed and FHA and VA financing! Great home at this price point! Visit today and move in before the snow flies!
